      "cooked": "<p>What I would like to do during next fall/winter is 16 weeks of training, divided into 4 blocks of 4 weeks each and each block.</p>\n<p>Four weeks of The Serious Italian<br>\nFour weeks of Crunche Power<br>\nFour weeks of Fitness Cyclist<br>\nFour weeks of Progessive Sweet Spot</p>\n<p>Is this idea as stupid as it sounds?</p>\n<p>I simply chose the first 4 \u201cBlock type\u201d but I\u2019am open to other blocks and ideas.</p>",
